6. Methodology

6.1. Design

Randomized controlled trial with 80 neighborhood councils in a single metropolitan area. To ensure generalizability, we use blocked randomization stratified by neighborhood socio‑economic status (SES) and racial composition. Within each block, groups are randomly assigned to treatment (LAD with AI) or control (existing meeting format).

